            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "But the president has another option. His purportedly tough regulators ‚Äî including Federal Trade Commission (FTC) Chairperson Lina Khan ‚Äî could use their authority to investigate potential illegal price increases or limits on production.",
